<subSubSection id="C368652E935F8E02F2FAFCFAFB5CFC26" pageId="6" pageNumber="490" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BCD36A5935F8E02F2FAFCFAFC98FC02" blockId="6.[151,1437,799,1006]" pageId="6" pageNumber="490">
Data to distinguish 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D26935F8E02F3A2FCFAFDA6FC4A" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1829" box="[415,631,872,897]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Harpalus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="490" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="punctatostriatus">
<emphasis id="B906EAB7935F8E02F3A2FCFAFDA6FC4A" box="[415,631,872,897]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="490">H. punctatostriatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D26935F8E02F087FCFAFCF2FC4A" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1829" box="[698,803,871,897]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Harpalus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="490" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="dispar">
<emphasis id="B906EAB7935F8E02F087FCFAFCF2FC4A" box="[698,803,871,897]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="490">H. dispar</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
are available for both the nominal 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D26935F8E02F69BFCFAFA8FFC4A" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1829" box="[1190,1374,871,897]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Harpalus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="490" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="dispar" subSpecies="dispar">
<emphasis id="B906EAB7935F8E02F69BFCFAFA8FFC4A" box="[1190,1374,871,897]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="490">H. dispar dispar</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(e.g., 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B54935F8E02F2AAFC1EFEFFFC6E" author="Fuente de la, J. M." box="[151,302,907,934]" pageId="6" pageNumber="490" refId="ref10490" refString="Fuente de la, J. M. (1927) Tablas analiticas para la clasificacion de los coleopteros de la Peninsula Iberica. Adephaga: I Cicindelidae, II Carabidae. J. Bosch, Barcelona, 415 pp." type="book" year="1927">Fuente, 1927</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B54935F8E02F306FC19FE06FC6E" author="Jeannel, R." box="[315,471,907,933]" pageId="6" pageNumber="490" pagination="572 - 1173" refId="ref11231" refString="Jeannel, R. (1942) Coleopteres carabiques. Deuxieme partie. Faune de France 40. Librairie de la Faculte des Sciences, Paris, pp. 572 - 1173." type="book chapter" year="1942">Jeannel, 1942</bibRefCitation>
) and the eastern populations of 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D26935F8E02F179FC1EFB29FC6E" authority="Menetries, 1832" authorityName="Menetries" authorityYear="1832" box="[836,1272,907,933]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Harpalus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="490" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="dispar" subSpecies="elegantulus">
<emphasis id="B906EAB7935F8E02F179FC1EFBE8FC6E" box="[836,1081,907,933]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="490">H. dispar elegantulus</emphasis>
Ménétriés, 1832
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D26935F8E02F70CFC1EFE4FFC02" authority="Gebler, 1830" authorityName="Gebler" authorityYear="1830" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Harpalus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="490" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="dispar" subSpecies="splendens">
<emphasis id="B906EAB7935F8E02F70CFC1EFED4FC02" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="490">H. dispar splendens</emphasis>
Gebler, 1830
</taxonomicName>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B54935F8E02F391FC3DFD78FC01" author="Kataev, B. M. &amp; Wrase, D. W." box="[428,681,943,970]" pageId="6" pageNumber="490" pagination="319 - 330" refId="ref11494" refString="Kataev, B. M. &amp; Wrase, D. W. (1995) Three new and two little-known Palearctic species of the genus Harpalus Latr. (Coleoptera, Carabidae). Linzer Biologische Beitrage, 27, 319 - 330." type="journal article" year="1995">Kataev &amp; Wrase 1995</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B54935F8E02F089FC22FCEFFC02" author="Wrase, D. W." box="[692,830,943,970]" pageId="6" pageNumber="490" refId="ref12634" refString="Wrase, D. W. (2011) Genus Tschitscherinellus. Arndt, E., Schnitter, P., Sfenthourakis, S. &amp; Wrase, D. W. (Eds.), Ground beetles (Carabidae) of Greece. Pensoft, Sofia, pp. 163." type="book" year="2011">Wrase 2011</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BCD36A5935F8E02F2FAFC41FB5CFC26" blockId="6.[151,1437,799,1006]" box="[199,1165,979,1006]" pageId="6" pageNumber="490">
This species is known from the whole Mediterranean Basin (
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B54935F8E02F152FC41FB50FC26" author="Kataev, B. M. &amp; Wrase, D. W." box="[879,1153,979,1006]" pageId="6" pageNumber="490" pagination="1810" refId="ref11718" refString="Kataev, B. M. &amp; Wrase, D. W. (2017 c) Subtribe Harpalina Bonelli, 1810. In: Lobl, I. &amp; Lobl, D. (Eds.), Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera. Vol. 1. Revised and Updated Edition. Brill, Leiden, pp. 515 - 562." type="book chapter" year="2017">Kataev &amp; Wrase, 2017c</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
